TITLE: Initializing Flagsmith Client in Dart
DESCRIPTION: Initialize the Flagsmith client with your API key and optional configuration. This snippet also demonstrates seeding default flag values and fetching updates from the API.
SOURCE: https://github.com/flagsmith/flagsmith/blob/main/docs/docs/clients/client-side/flutter.md#2025-04-21_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: dart
CODE:
```
import 'package:flagsmith/flagsmith.dart';

