TITLE: Subscribing to Flag Updates in Flagsmith Swift SDK
DESCRIPTION: This code demonstrates how to listen for real-time flag updates using the 'flagStream' property. It uses Swift's async/await pattern to handle updates and dispatches UI updates to the main queue.
SOURCE: https://github.com/flagsmith/flagsmith/blob/main/docs/docs/clients/client-side/ios.mdx#2025-04-21_snippet_15

LANGUAGE: swift
CODE:
```
func subscribeToFlagUpdates() {
    Task {
        for await updatedFlags in flagsmith.flagStream {
            DispatchQueue.main.async {
                flags = updatedFlags
            }
        }
    }
}
```

