TITLE: InfluxDB API Request Downsampling Task
DESCRIPTION: InfluxDB task configuration to downsample API request data to 15-minute blocks for improved query performance. Aggregates data from the default bucket into downsampled measurements.
SOURCE: https://github.com/flagsmith/flagsmith/blob/main/docs/docs/deployment/index.md#2025-04-21_snippet_8

LANGUAGE: text
CODE:
```
option task = {name: "Downsample (API Requests)", every: 15m}

data = from(bucket: "default")
 |> range(start: -duration(v: int(v: task.every) * 2))
 |> filter(fn: (r) =>
  (r._measurement == "api_call"))

data
 |> aggregateWindow(fn: sum, every: 15m)
 |> filter(fn: (r) =>
  (exists r._value))
 |> to(bucket: "default_downsampled_15m")
```

